io.github.mrblobman.nbt

Class NBTListTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.mrblobman.nbt.NBTBaseTag<NBTListTag>
      • io.github.mrblobman.nbt.NBTListTag

  • public abstract class NBTListTag
extends NBTBaseTag<NBTListTag>
    An NBTListTag is a collection of NBTBaseTags of the same type. It is a special NBTBaseTag in the sense that its value (returned by NBTBaseTag.get()) is itself. The value is determined
